            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-12-31T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-01-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="311" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d311">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On October 22, 1947, the Department of State released <hi rend="italic">The Greek
                        Aid Program</hi> as Publication No. 2939. The publication reviewed the
                    matters of “Why Help Greece?”, “What Kind of Assistance Does Greece Need?”,
                    “What Our Money Will Be Spent for”, “Our Advisory Mission in Greece”, and “The
                    Measure of Success”.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
